<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="depend-on">depend on</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-rely-on-upon">1.★ <strong>依靠；依赖(rely on / upon)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>depend on</strong> energy <strong>to</strong> do many things in our daily lives.  
在日常生活中，我们做很多事都离不开能源。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If our parents do everything for us children, we won’t learn to depend on ourselves. 
如果父母替我们这些孩子做所有的事情，我们就学不会独立。</p><footer>2010 上海</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>depend on</strong> him <strong>finishing</strong> the job this weekend.
我们指望他这个周末能完成工作。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>相信；信赖：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Depend upon it, we shall solve the problem at last.
请相信，我们最终会解决这个问题。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You can depend on Jane — she always keeps her promises. 
你可以信赖简，她总是信守诺言。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>由…决定；取决于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How much sleep you need depends a lot on your age.
你需要多少睡眠主要取决于你的年龄。</p><footer>2017 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The journey takes about two hours, depending on traffic.  
旅途大约需要两小时，这取决于交通状况。</p><footer>2011 上海</footer></div></div>